{"tid":1532173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下一步，就係要迫癲班狗","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:47:22.000Z","uid":185713,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e216e3b0e60d900c2616ade5a9df3def622658","tid":1532173,"uid":185713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"大家都知道佢地要成日ot冇咩時間休息，大家都睇到佢地對啲市民黎罵，亂柒咁拉人打人，上網都睇唔小發癲打自己人亂射催淚彈等等。我地要做係進一步迫癲班黑警<br />\n小弟得出2個方法去令到佢地精神緊張<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>方法1：就係不停話「阿sir,跌左支槍呀！」or子彈</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">因對佢地黎講會好緊張<br />\nfake，佢地又信又可以笑鳩佢地<br />\n如是這，玩多兩玩，狼來了，佢地唔信，真係跌左<br />\n佢地把槍就byebye<br />\n合適情況：市民圍黑警，屌佢地個時，可以咁講，特別係佢地走果時</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>方法2：就係咁大聲講，「喂，自己人呀」，「伙記」</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">知道自己即將被捕，或啲狗已經捉住你<br />\n你可以咁講，等佢地拉你果時爭取時間比你走<br />\n同時要佢地難分真與假，到時拉左自己人就好笑</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKbadguys/videos/389481578293487/UzpfSTEwMDAxMjA5ODYyNTY4ODo3MTU2MDY4NDIxODU5MzA/?id=100012098625688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKbadguys%2Fvideos%2F389481578293487%2FUzpfSTEwMDAxMjA5ODYyNTY4ODo3MTU2MDY4NDIxODU5MzA%2F%3Fid%3D100012098625688&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ao%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=5ce8a807\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKbadguys/videos/389481578293487/UzpfSTEwMDAxMjA5ODYyNTY4ODo3MTU2MDY4NDIxODU5MzA/?id=100012098625688</a>"},{"pid":"cb84e5ac681e9649c0c2738b8b667d670fad929a","tid":1532173,"uid":185713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"754d9b4537cd33f46371fbc82c22f715eb127b11","tid":1532173,"uid":241776,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:41:15.000Z","msg":"同埋狗仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umKHYu2.jpg\" data-thumbn